StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetDocumentLastVersion]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@DocTypeID int, @RssOrgId int, @year int
AS BEGIN
SELECT Max(DocumentUpload.ChangeVer) FROM DocumentUpload WHERE (DocumentTypeID = @DocTypeID OR @DocTypeID IS NULL) AND (RssOrgId = @RssOrgId OR @RssOrgId IS NULL) AND (YearFor = @year OR @year IS NULL)
END
